### 3. Listar Todos los Tickets (Solo Admins)
GET http://localhost:8001/tickets
Authorization: Bearer a705cb6d024e0b43c29d10092a909b14
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Ver Detalles de un Ticket
# Gestor:solo sus tickets | Admin: todos
GET http://localhost:8001/tickets/1
Authorization: Bearer a705cb6d024e0b43c29d10092a909b14
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Actualizar Estado de un Ticket (Solo Admins)
PUT http://localhost:8001/tickets/1/status
Authorization: Bearer a705cb6d024e0b43c29d10092a909b14
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "estado": "en_progreso"
}

### 6. Asignar Ticket a un Admin (Solo Admins)
PUT http://localhost:8001/tickets/1/assign
Authorization: Bearer a705cb6d024e0b43c29d10092a909b14
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "admin_id": 3
}
